  "id": "RAW_f8e3c2",
  "title": "Qwen3 Embedding：基于基础模型的文本嵌入与重排序技术，附技术报告英中 PDF 对照版",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5ODkzMzMwMQ==&mid=2650449102&idx=2&sn=2858b91d380dd3e183ce5216acc950a9",
  "date": "2025-06-06 11:11:00",
  "author": "NLPer",
  "siteName": "AINLP",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/1df5769f-f90a-440d-116a-24c1fdb89900/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.40404040404040403\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"990\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"502965208\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/1df5769f-f90a-440d-116a-24c1fdb89900/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">今天阿里通义千问团队</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">开源了Qwen3 Embedding系列模型，并</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">发布了《Qwen3 Embedding: Advancing Text Embedding and Reranking Through Foundation Models》技术报告，介绍了 Qwen3 Embedding 系列模型。该模型在文本嵌入和重排序领域取得了显著进步，为自然语言处理（NLP）和信息检索应用提供了强大的工具。</span></span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;font-size:18px;font-variant-east-asian:inherit;font-variation-settings:inherit;font-variant-position:inherit;text-decoration-thickness:initial;word-spacing:0px;font-variant-alternates:inherit;scrollbar-color:transparent transparent;text-indent:0px;font-variant-emoji:inherit;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, sans-serif;font-variant-numeric:inherit;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start;border:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;letter-spacing:0px;vertical-align:baseline;line-height:28px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;font-stretch:inherit;font-kerning:inherit;font-optical-sizing:inherit;text-transform:none;font-size-adjust:inherit;font-feature-settings:inherit;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">背景知识</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">文本嵌入和重排序是多项 NLP 和信息检索应用的基础组件，如网络搜索、问答系统和推荐系统等。高质量的嵌入可以使模型捕捉文本之间的语义关系，而有效的重排序机制则确保将最相关的结果优先展示。随着大型语言模型（LLMs）的出现，文本嵌入和重排序模型得到了进一步发展。然而，训练在可扩展性、上下文理解和与特定下游任务对齐方面表现出色的嵌入和重排序模型仍然具有挑战性。</span></span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;font-size:18px;font-variant-east-asian:inherit;font-variation-settings:inherit;font-variant-position:inherit;text-decoration-thickness:initial;word-spacing:0px;font-variant-alternates:inherit;scrollbar-color:transparent transparent;text-indent:0px;font-variant-emoji:inherit;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, sans-serif;font-variant-numeric:inherit;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start;border:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;letter-spacing:0px;vertical-align:baseline;line-height:28px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;font-stretch:inherit;font-kerning:inherit;font-optical-sizing:inherit;text-transform:none;font-size-adjust:inherit;font-feature-settings:inherit;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">研究方法</span></span></h2>\n  <h3 style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;font-size:16px;font-variant-east-asian:inherit;font-variation-settings:inherit;font-variant-position:inherit;text-decoration-thickness:initial;word-spacing:0px;font-variant-alternates:inherit;scrollbar-color:transparent transparent;text-indent:0px;font-variant-emoji:inherit;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, sans-serif;font-variant-numeric:inherit;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start;border:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;letter-spacing:0px;vertical-align:baseline;line-height:26px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;font-stretch:inherit;font-kerning:inherit;font-optical-sizing:inherit;text-transform:none;font-size-adjust:inherit;font-feature-settings:inherit;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Qwen3 基础模型</span></span></h3>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Qwen3 Embedding 系列基于 Qwen3 基础模型构建。Qwen3 基础模型具备强大的多语言文本理解和生成能力，为嵌入和重排序模型的训练提供了坚实的基础。</span></span></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;font-size:16px;font-variant-east-asian:inherit;font-variation-settings:inherit;font-variant-position:inherit;text-decoration-thickness:initial;word-spacing:0px;font-variant-alternates:inherit;scrollbar-color:transparent transparent;text-indent:0px;font-variant-emoji:inherit;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, sans-serif;font-variant-numeric:inherit;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start;border:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;letter-spacing:0px;vertical-align:baseline;line-height:26px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;font-stretch:inherit;font-kerning:inherit;font-optical-sizing:inherit;text-transform:none;font-size-adjust:inherit;font-feature-settings:inherit;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">多阶段训练流程</span></span></h3>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Qwen3 Embedding 系列采用多阶段训练流程，包括大规模无监督预训练和在高质量数据集上的监督微调。此外，还采用模型融合策略，将多个模型检查点合并，以增强模型的鲁棒性和适应性。</span></span></p>\n  <ol style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:14px;font-variant-east-asian:inherit;font-variation-settings:inherit;font-variant-position:inherit;text-decoration-thickness:initial;word-spacing:0px;font-variant-alternates:inherit;scrollbar-color:transparent transparent;text-indent:0px;font-variant-emoji:inherit;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, sans-serif;font-variant-numeric:inherit;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;list-style:decimal;text-align:start;border:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 24px;margin:0px 0px 16px;letter-spacing:0.5px;vertical-align:baseline;line-height:inherit;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;font-stretch:inherit;font-kerning:inherit;font-optical-sizing:inherit;text-transform:none;font-size-adjust:inherit;font-feature-settings:inherit;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"font: inherit;scrollbar-color: transparent transparent;margin: 0px 0px 12px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;\">\n    <p><strong style=\"font-family: inherit;scrollbar-color: transparent transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-weight: 600;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-optical-sizing: inherit;font-size-adjust: inherit;font-kerning: inherit;font-feature-settings: inherit;font-variation-settings: inherit;vertical-align: baseline;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">无监督预训练</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">：利用 Qwen3 指令模型合成大规模、高质量、多语言和多任务的文本相关性数据集。这些合成数据用于初始的无监督训练阶段。</span></span></p></li>\n   <li style=\"font: inherit;scrollbar-color: transparent transparent;margin: 0px 0px 12px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;\">\n    <p><strong style=\"font-family: inherit;scrollbar-color: transparent transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-weight: 600;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-optical-sizing: inherit;font-size-adjust: inherit;font-kerning: inherit;font-feature-settings: inherit;font-variation-settings: inherit;vertical-align: baseline;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">监督微调</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">：从合成数据中筛选出高质量的小规模数据用于监督训练阶段。这一阶段使用基于 InfoNCE 框架的改进对比损失函数进行优化。</span></span></p></li>\n   <li style=\"font: inherit;scrollbar-color: transparent transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;\">\n    <p><strong style=\"font-family: inherit;scrollbar-color: transparent transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-weight: 600;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-optical-sizing: inherit;font-size-adjust: inherit;font-kerning: inherit;font-feature-settings: inherit;font-variation-settings: inherit;vertical-align: baseline;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">模型融合</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">：使用球面线性插值（slerp）技术，将监督微调过程中保存的多个模型检查点合并，以提升模型在不同数据分布上的鲁棒性和泛化性能。</span></span></p></li>\n  </ol>\n  <h3 style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;font-size:16px;font-variant-east-asian:inherit;font-variation-settings:inherit;font-variant-position:inherit;text-decoration-thickness:initial;word-spacing:0px;font-variant-alternates:inherit;scrollbar-color:transparent transparent;text-indent:0px;font-variant-emoji:inherit;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, sans-serif;font-variant-numeric:inherit;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start;border:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;letter-spacing:0px;vertical-align:baseline;line-height:26px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;font-stretch:inherit;font-kerning:inherit;font-optical-sizing:inherit;text-transform:none;font-size-adjust:inherit;font-feature-settings:inherit;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">嵌入模型架构</span></span></h3>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Qwen3 嵌入模型基于 Qwen3 基础模型的密集版本构建，有 0.6B、4B 和 8B 三种参数规模。模型通过因果注意力机制处理输入序列，并在序列末尾添加 [EOS] 令牌。最终嵌入从最后一层对应 [EOS] 令牌的隐藏状态中获取。为了使嵌入在下游任务中遵循指令，将指令与查询拼接为一个输入上下文，而文档保持不变。</span></span></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;font-size:16px;font-variant-east-asian:inherit;font-variation-settings:inherit;font-variant-position:inherit;text-decoration-thickness:initial;word-spacing:0px;font-variant-alternates:inherit;scrollbar-color:transparent transparent;text-indent:0px;font-variant-emoji:inherit;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, sans-serif;font-variant-numeric:inherit;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start;border:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;letter-spacing:0px;vertical-align:baseline;line-height:26px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;font-stretch:inherit;font-kerning:inherit;font-optical-sizing:inherit;text-transform:none;font-size-adjust:inherit;font-feature-settings:inherit;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">重排序模型架构</span></span></h3>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Qwen3 重排序模型同样基于 Qwen3 基础模型的密集版本构建，有 0.6B、4B 和 8B 三种参数规模。模型使用 LLM 聊天模板，将相似度评估任务视为二元分类问题。输入遵循特定模板，模型通过计算下一个令牌为“是”或“否”的可能性来确定相关性分数。</span></span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;font-size:18px;font-variant-east-asian:inherit;font-variation-settings:inherit;font-variant-position:inherit;text-decoration-thickness:initial;word-spacing:0px;font-variant-alternates:inherit;scrollbar-color:transparent transparent;text-indent:0px;font-variant-emoji:inherit;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, sans-serif;font-variant-numeric:inherit;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start;border:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;letter-spacing:0px;vertical-align:baseline;line-height:28px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;font-stretch:inherit;font-kerning:inherit;font-optical-sizing:inherit;text-transform:none;font-size-adjust:inherit;font-feature-settings:inherit;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">实验评估</span></span></h2>\n  <h3 style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;font-size:16px;font-variant-east-asian:inherit;font-variation-settings:inherit;font-variant-position:inherit;text-decoration-thickness:initial;word-spacing:0px;font-variant-alternates:inherit;scrollbar-color:transparent transparent;text-indent:0px;font-variant-emoji:inherit;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, sans-serif;font-variant-numeric:inherit;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start;border:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;letter-spacing:0px;vertical-align:baseline;line-height:26px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;font-stretch:inherit;font-kerning:inherit;font-optical-sizing:inherit;text-transform:none;font-size-adjust:inherit;font-feature-settings:inherit;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">评估基准</span></span></h3>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Qwen3 嵌入模型在多个基准测试中进行了全面评估，包括大规模多语言文本嵌入基准（MMTEB）、MTEB（英语、v2）、CMTEB 和 MTEB（代码）等。评估涵盖文本检索、分类、语义文本相似性等多种任务。</span></span></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;font-size:16px;font-variant-east-asian:inherit;font-variation-settings:inherit;font-variant-position:inherit;text-decoration-thickness:initial;word-spacing:0px;font-variant-alternates:inherit;scrollbar-color:transparent transparent;text-indent:0px;font-variant-emoji:inherit;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, sans-serif;font-variant-numeric:inherit;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start;border:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;letter-spacing:0px;vertical-align:baseline;line-height:26px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;font-stretch:inherit;font-kerning:inherit;font-optical-sizing:inherit;text-transform:none;font-size-adjust:inherit;font-feature-settings:inherit;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">主要结果</span></span></h3>\n  <ol style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:14px;font-variant-east-asian:inherit;font-variation-settings:inherit;font-variant-position:inherit;text-decoration-thickness:initial;word-spacing:0px;font-variant-alternates:inherit;scrollbar-color:transparent transparent;text-indent:0px;font-variant-emoji:inherit;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, sans-serif;font-variant-numeric:inherit;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;list-style:decimal;text-align:start;border:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 24px;margin:0px 0px 16px;letter-spacing:0.5px;vertical-align:baseline;line-height:inherit;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;font-stretch:inherit;font-kerning:inherit;font-optical-sizing:inherit;text-transform:none;font-size-adjust:inherit;font-feature-settings:inherit;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"font: inherit;scrollbar-color: transparent transparent;margin: 0px 0px 12px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;\">\n    <p><strong style=\"font-family: inherit;scrollbar-color: transparent transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-weight: 600;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-optical-sizing: inherit;font-size-adjust: inherit;font-kerning: inherit;font-feature-settings: inherit;font-variation-settings: inherit;vertical-align: baseline;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">嵌入模型</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">：Qwen3-Embedding-4B 和 8B 模型在 MMTEB 评估中表现最佳。即使是最小的 Qwen3-Embedding-0.6B 模型，仅拥有 0.6B 参数，其性能也仅略低于表现最佳的基线方法（Gemini-Embedding），与 gte-Qwen2-7B-instruct 具有竞争力。</span></span></p></li>\n   <li style=\"font: inherit;scrollbar-color: transparent transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;\">\n    <p><strong style=\"font-family: inherit;scrollbar-color: transparent transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-weight: 600;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-optical-sizing: inherit;font-size-adjust: inherit;font-kerning: inherit;font-feature-settings: inherit;font-variation-settings: inherit;vertical-align: baseline;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">重排序模型</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">：所有三个 Qwen3 重排序模型相较于嵌入模型均提升了性能，并超越了所有基线重排序方法。Qwen3-Reranker-8B 模型在大多数任务中表现最佳，相较于 0.6B 模型，在多个任务中排名结果提高了 3.0 分。</span></span></p></li>\n  </ol>\n  <h3 style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;font-size:16px;font-variant-east-asian:inherit;font-variation-settings:inherit;font-variant-position:inherit;text-decoration-thickness:initial;word-spacing:0px;font-variant-alternates:inherit;scrollbar-color:transparent transparent;text-indent:0px;font-variant-emoji:inherit;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, sans-serif;font-variant-numeric:inherit;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start;border:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;letter-spacing:0px;vertical-align:baseline;line-height:26px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;font-stretch:inherit;font-kerning:inherit;font-optical-sizing:inherit;text-transform:none;font-size-adjust:inherit;font-feature-settings:inherit;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">分析</span></span></h3>\n  <ol style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:14px;font-variant-east-asian:inherit;font-variation-settings:inherit;font-variant-position:inherit;text-decoration-thickness:initial;word-spacing:0px;font-variant-alternates:inherit;scrollbar-color:transparent transparent;text-indent:0px;font-variant-emoji:inherit;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, sans-serif;font-variant-numeric:inherit;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;list-style:decimal;text-align:start;border:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 24px;margin:0px 0px 16px;letter-spacing:0.5px;vertical-align:baseline;line-height:inherit;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;font-stretch:inherit;font-kerning:inherit;font-optical-sizing:inherit;text-transform:none;font-size-adjust:inherit;font-feature-settings:inherit;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"font: inherit;scrollbar-color: transparent transparent;margin: 0px 0px 12px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;\">\n    <p><strong style=\"font-family: inherit;scrollbar-color: transparent transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-weight: 600;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-optical-sizing: inherit;font-size-adjust: inherit;font-kerning: inherit;font-feature-settings: inherit;font-variation-settings: inherit;vertical-align: baseline;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">大规模弱监督预训练的有效性</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">：仅在合成数据上训练的 Qwen3-Embedding-0.6B 模型相较于最终模型表现出了合理的性能。如果进一步去除弱监督训练阶段，最终性能明显下降，表明大规模弱监督训练阶段对于实现卓越性能至关重要。</span></span></p></li>\n   <li style=\"font: inherit;scrollbar-color: transparent transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;\">\n    <p><strong style=\"font-family: inherit;scrollbar-color: transparent transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-weight: 600;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-optical-sizing: inherit;font-size-adjust: inherit;font-kerning: inherit;font-feature-settings: inherit;font-variation-settings: inherit;vertical-align: baseline;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">模型融合的有效性</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">：未采用模型融合技术训练的模型性能明显不如采用模型融合的最终 Qwen3-Embedding-0.6B 模型，表明模型融合阶段对于开发强大的模型至关重要。</span></span></p></li>\n  </ol>\n  <h2 style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;font-size:18px;font-variant-east-asian:inherit;font-variation-settings:inherit;font-variant-position:inherit;text-decoration-thickness:initial;word-spacing:0px;font-variant-alternates:inherit;scrollbar-color:transparent transparent;text-indent:0px;font-variant-emoji:inherit;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, sans-serif;font-variant-numeric:inherit;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start;border:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;letter-spacing:0px;vertical-align:baseline;line-height:28px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;font-stretch:inherit;font-kerning:inherit;font-optical-sizing:inherit;text-transform:none;font-size-adjust:inherit;font-feature-settings:inherit;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">关键结论</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Qwen3 Embedding 系列模型基于 Qwen3 基础模型，通过多阶段训练流程、合成数据和模型融合策略，在文本嵌入和重排序任务中取得了最先进的性能。这些模型在多语言检索、代码检索和复杂指令遵循等任务中表现出色，并且在多个基准测试中超越了现有的开源模型和商业 API 服务。Qwen3 Embedding 和 Qwen3 重排序模型（0.6B、4B 和 8B）已开源，可供社区使用和进一步开发。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">通过这篇技术报告，我们深入解析了 Qwen3 Embedding 系列模型的设计、训练方法和实验评估。这一模型的出现为文本嵌入和重排序领域带来了新的突破，有望在众多 NLP 和信息检索应用中发挥重要作用。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;display:inline !important;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;float:none;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;Work Sans&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:left;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\">附</span><span leaf=\"\">Qwen3 Embedding</span><span leaf=\"\">技术报告英中对照版，仅供学习参考，感兴趣的朋友关注AGI之美公众号，回复'qwen3em'获取全文PDF：</span></span></p>\n  <section class=\"mp_profile_iframe_wrp\" nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\">\n   <mp-common-profile class=\"js_uneditable custom_select_card mp_profile_iframe\" data-pluginname=\"mpprofile\" data-nickname=\"AGI之美\" data-alias=\"AGIBeauty\" data-from=\"0\" data-headimg=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/ZvlMsfNDDjn34KPcic6DsUzFOaXUI4TgaiaCu2jpFTr4U6LzwAFuWYQb4D7qzQ3YTIfqSmLFd2qp1wY0TLRyETVA/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-signature=\"通用人工智能（AGI）曙光已现，AGI比想象中来得更快，让我们一起迎接AGI时代！\" data-id=\"MzI2MzI4MTQ5MA==\" data-is_biz_ban=\"0\" data-service_type=\"1\" data-verify_status=\"0\"></mp-common-profile>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-imgfileid=\"100001112\" data-ratio=\"1.2935185185185185\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8690b1c6-4ace-49ac-fe6d-011d787cad00/public\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8690b1c6-4ace-49ac-fe6d-011d787cad00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a184fca3-e4fa-49de-54cc-392e702b9300/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1.2935185185185185\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100001113\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a184fca3-e4fa-49de-54cc-392e702b9300/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/94d7fe12-9530-4e45-423a-25392bb3b300/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1.2935185185185185\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100001116\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/94d7fe12-9530-4e45-423a-25392bb3b300/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-imgfileid=\"100001115\" data-ratio=\"1.2935185185185185\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a1973aeb-5ca1-403f-dc15-22f938c46c00/public\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a1973aeb-5ca1-403f-dc15-22f938c46c00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4cbf9cb8-b178-4a28-163c-9b4a27c3ed00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1.2935185185185185\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100001114\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4cbf9cb8-b178-4a28-163c-9b4a27c3ed00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-imgfileid=\"100001117\" data-ratio=\"1.2935185185185185\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/2c99f1fa-cc29-4c4e-a6d7-2ac72a4ab500/public\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/2c99f1fa-cc29-4c4e-a6d7-2ac72a4ab500/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"3 1 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;display:inline !important;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;float:none;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;Work Sans&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:left;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\">感兴趣的朋友关注AGI之美公众号，回复'qwen3em'获取全文PDF：</span></span></p>\n  <section class=\"mp_profile_iframe_wrp\" nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\">\n   <mp-common-profile class=\"js_uneditable custom_select_card mp_profile_iframe\" data-pluginname=\"mpprofile\" data-nickname=\"AGI之美\" data-alias=\"AGIBeauty\" data-from=\"2\" data-headimg=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/ZvlMsfNDDjn34KPcic6DsUzFOaXUI4TgaiaCu2jpFTr4U6LzwAFuWYQb4D7qzQ3YTIfqSmLFd2qp1wY0TLRyETVA/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-signature=\"通用人工智能（AGI）曙光已现，AGI比想象中来得更快，让我们一起迎接AGI时代！\" data-id=\"MzI2MzI4MTQ5MA==\" data-is_biz_ban=\"0\" data-service_type=\"1\" data-verify_status=\"0\"></mp-common-profile>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "阿里开源 Qwen3 Embedding 模型，通过多阶段训练实现文本嵌入和重排序 SOTA 性能。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "阿里开源 Qwen3 Embedding 模型，通过多阶段训练实现文本嵌入和重排序 SOTA 性能。",
  "summary": "文章介绍了阿里通义千问团队开源的 Qwen3 Embedding 系列模型及其技术报告。该系列模型基于 Qwen3 基础模型构建，采用无监督预训练、监督微调和模型融合的多阶段训练流程，利用合成数据增强性能。模型包括 0.6B、4B、8B 不同规模的嵌入模型和重排序模型，分别基于因果注意力机制和聊天模板实现。实验评估显示，Qwen3 Embedding 和 Reranker 模型在 MMTEB 等多项基准测试中表现出色，超越了现有开源及部分商业模型。文章强调大规模弱监督预训练和模型融合对性能提升的关键作用，并指出这些模型已开源，为 NLP 和信息检索应用提供了强大工具。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "Qwen3 Embedding 和 Reranker 模型在多个基准测试中达到或超越 SOTA 水平",
      "explanation": "0.6B 至 8B 规模的模型在多语言文本嵌入和重排序任务上表现突出，性能优于不少现有模型和商业 API，为 NLP 应用提供强力基础。"
    },
    {
      "point": "模型采用多阶段训练流程，包括合成数据预训练和模型融合",
      "explanation": "利用大规模合成数据进行无监督预训练，结合监督微调和模型融合，显著提升了模型的鲁棒性和泛化能力，是性能关键。"
    },
    {
      "point": "模型基于 Qwen3 基础模型构建，并已开源",
      "explanation": "利用强大基础模型的理解能力，提供不同规模的版本，并通过开源促进社区进一步使用和开发，降低技术应用门槛。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "今天阿里通义千问团队开源了 Qwen3 Embedding 系列模型，并发布了《Qwen3 Embedding: Advancing Text Embedding and Reranking Through Foundation Models》技术报告，介绍了 Qwen3 Embedding 系列模型。",
    "Qwen3 Embedding 系列采用多阶段训练流程，包括大规模无监督预训练和在高质量数据集上的监督微调。",
    "Qwen3-Embedding-4B 和 8B 模型在 MMTEB 评估中表现最佳。",
    "所有三个 Qwen3 重排序模型相较于嵌入模型均提升了性能，并超越了所有基线重排序方法。",
    "大规模弱监督训练阶段对于实现卓越性能至关重要。"
  ],
